dcterms:description: A remote sensing-based spatio-temporal dataset consisting of four classes: construction, destruction, cultivation, and de-cultivation. It contains temporal samples from the years 2011, 2013, and 2017 from Digital Globe, covering approximately 5310 km2.
dcterms:title: C2D2

dcterms:creator: A. Z. et al.
dcterms:description: A dataset for surgical visual domain adaptation consisting of three class classification tasks: needle-driving, dissection, and knot-tying. The training data includes 476 total videos, with a mix of virtual reality and real-time clinical data.
dcterms:title: SurgVisDom
